::Feline::

She walked out of the messhall, gracefully moving her feline figure 
as she walked.  She walked down the hall and towards the bridge.  She 
was wondering if Chordate would ever take her on that tour he 
promised her.  She wondered if he was on the bridge or not.  She 
walked around and finally came to the bridge.  She turned the corner 
and stood in the doorway.  She looked around.  If Chordate would not 
escort her around, the she would get another bot to do it.  She 
needed more parts for, 'just in case'. She had no idea if the others 
had started thier search for Dinotbot and Travatron.  Or what 
condition they might be in when they arrive.  She looked and hoped to 
find a nice bot to show her around and help gather parts.
